{
  "stem": "26609.20",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But she's very inquisitive, my daughter, and always very intelligent.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She was-- it was at night time-- in a bed together with-- there were two children together-- a bed that was not a bed.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was on the ground in racks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And as she heard [INAUDIBLE], she got up her head and listened.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She said, what is it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The others lied there, and they didn't-- at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were not interested.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But she got--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he went up with the sack, put her into a sack like a little animal over his back and ran out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As he ran out, she started scream, I'll go to the Jews and I'll tell them that the mother told me that-- then said yes-- the mother told me that I can keep her if she's killed.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the mother is killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was much before.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I want-- and took stones and threw the stones at--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But he said, all right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I am the police.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you do it again, we'll put you into prison.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wasn't true at all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that woman was a Jewish woman, you know, that he-- I met later.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Straightaway he said, I'll take you to my place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She paid him, she was in his place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she started to scream, I want to go back to my [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I want to my-- I don't want Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You'll kill me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She told me later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is the whole story.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I asked her, is it true, [INAUDIBLE]?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she said, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was told like this, and I didn't know anything else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I know that the Jews killed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, but the Germans killed, not the Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She told me the Jews, and I hated the Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
